<h3 id="4-dahlia">4. Dahlia</h3>
<ul>
  <li>That being the case, these flowers make the best gift for someone you admire or perceive as a strong person.</li>
  <li>If you know anyone who’s experiencing a significant change in life, dahlias are the perfect flower to express support, good luck, or congratulations since they mean embracing positive changes. Other known dahlia flower meanings include commitment and honesty. So, if you want to let someone special know that you are committed, then dahlia flowers are worth considering[3]. 
<img src="/images/friend04.jpg" alt="" />
<br /></li>
</ul>

